Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:24.42,00:20:26.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これは水牢の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Water Prison Jutsu!
