Dialogue: 0,00:20:38.87,00:20:41.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ヤマト）しまった！？\N海のほうへ行ったよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's making its way\Ntowards the ocean!
